---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
const lastUpdated = '2026-01-12';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now | Ayamatma" description="What I'm focused on right now." lang={lang}>
  <section class="section stack">
    <h1 class="section-title">Now</h1>
    <p class="muted">What I'm focused on right now. <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">What's a now page?</a></p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="prose now-content">
      <p class="now-updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <h2>Building Ayamatma</h2>
      <p>
        This site is my primary focus. Writing essays that apply Protocol I (Primary Sources) rigor —
        every claim traced to śruti, every term defined with precision. Currently working on translations
        in Hindi and Telugu to make Vedānta accessible beyond English.
      </p>

      <h2>Reading</h2>
      <p>
        Re-reading Śaṅkara's Bhāṣya on Brahma Sūtra. Slowly. One sūtra per sitting.
        Also exploring where modern physics (quantum field theory, thermodynamics)
        genuinely parallels Vedāntic insight — and where the parallels are forced.
      </p>

      <h2>Practice</h2>
      <p>
        Daily meditation. Not guided apps. Just sitting. Watching the watcher.
        The gap between parokṣa (intellectual knowing) and aparokṣa (direct knowing)
        is the real work.
      </p>

      <h2>Not Doing</h2>
      <p>
        Not on social media. Not building an audience. Not monetizing.
        This site exists because jijñāsā is ānanda — the desire to know is bliss.
        That's enough.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="quote-block">
      <p class="sanskrit">कालः पचति भूतानि</p>
      <p class="english">Time cooks all beings.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .now-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent-cool);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .now-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .now-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .now-updated {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem !important;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
</style>
